<p>更新:<br>找到一个相关的资料: <a href="http://23pin.logdown.com/posts/161140-api17-inside-the-listview-item-using-relativelayout-attention" target="_blank" rel="external">http://23pin.logdown.com/posts/161140-api17-inside-the-listview-item-using-relativelayout-attention</a></p>
